org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection

Class CriticalBacktrackSelection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.BacktrackSelection
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.heuristics.selection.CriticalBacktrackSelection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NeighbourSelection<Request,Enrollment>, InfoProvider<Request,Enrollment>, SolverListener<Request,Enrollment>

    public class CriticalBacktrackSelection
extends BacktrackSelection
    Use backtrack neighbour selection. For all unassigned variables (in a random order) that are marked as critical, RandomizedBacktrackNeighbourSelection is being used.
